Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "aws_appstream_fleet" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name          = "<example_resource_name>"
  instance_type = "stream.standard.small"
  image_name    = "<IMAGE_NAME>"

  compute_capacity {
    desired_instances = 1
  }

  idle_disconnect_timeout_in_seconds = 600  # 重要：<= 10 分を強制してチェックを通過します
}
```
